high_descs: Turn around and walk to the shelves then turn right and walk to the counter between the toaster and coffee maker.
Open the cabinet to the left of the dish washer and pick up the glass down there and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Wash the glass in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the shelves in the corner in front of you.
Put the glass all the way to the right of the sponge on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn around and go toward the shelves, then turn right and go forward to the counter, then look down.
Open the cabinet adjacent to the dishwasher and take out the glass.
Turn right and move forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Clean the glass in the sink.
Turn left and move forward to the counter, then turn left and go straight to the shelves across the room.
Place the glass on the middle shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn left twice and walk toward the window, then turn right at the end of the island bar and walk to the dishwasher.
Take the glass out of the lower cabinet to the left of the dishwasher.
Move to your right to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink, rinse it off, then take it out.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf in the corner by the window.
Put the glass on the shelf with the bowl and the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass on the brown shelf with a bowl and a sponge.
